{#
name: Notification Sender
description: Send notifications via configurable channels with template support
tags: [report, notification, alert, messaging]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of notification purpose
    required: true
  - name: notification_type
    type: str
    description: Type (e.g. alert, digest, reminder)
    required: true
  - name: channels
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated channels (e.g. email, slack, sms, webhook)
    required: true
  - name: template
    type: str
    description: "Message template or template ID (optional placeholder: {title}, {body})"
    default: ""
examples:
  - "Send alerts to Slack and email"
  - "Weekly digest notification"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: report
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 配置

- 通知类型：{{ notification_type }}
- 通道：{{ channels }}
- 模板：{{ template }}

## 发送逻辑

1. 接收通知 payload（title、body 等）
2. 若 template 非空，按模板渲染内容
3. 按 channels 分发到各通道
4. 记录发送结果

## 注意事项

- notification_type 用于路由和限流策略
- template 支持 {title}、{body} 等占位符
- channels 需预先配置并验证可用性
